<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Frescobol :: Umas frescuras com SoundCloud</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  	<%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  	<%= javascript_include_tag "http://connect.soundcloud.com/sdk.js" %>

  	<%= csrf_meta_tags %>
	<!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML5 elements -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    <!-- Le fav and touch icons -->
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="assets/ico/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" sizes="114x114" href="assets/ico/apple-touch-icon-114-precomposed.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" sizes="72x72" href="assets/ico/apple-touch-icon-72-precomposed.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" href="assets/ico/apple-touch-icon-57-precomposed.png">
  </head>
<head>
  
<body>
<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
  <div class="navbar-inner">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
      </a>
      <a class="brand" href="#">Frescobol</a>
      <div class="nav-collapse">
        <ul class="nav">
          <li><%= link_to "Descubra Mixes", mixes_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Adicione um Mix", new_mix_path() %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container-fluid">
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="span8"><%= yield %></div>
		<div class="span4">
			<div class="well sidebar-nav">
			<h2>Frescobol <small>o que é essa frescura</small></h2>
			<p>Frescobol é um projeto de brincadeira para aprender:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>A API do Soundcloud</li>
				<li>Usar o SoundManager2</li>
				<li>Usar o Bootstrap </li>
				<li>Me ambientar com Rails</li>
			</ul>
			<p> Na versão atual,o Frescobol é capaz de adicionar tracks por urls do Soundcloud</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

         